# Kaamelott fortunes

Generates a [fortune](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fortune_(Unix)) package file from the the french quotes in [wikiquote](https://fr.wikiquote.org/wiki)
By defaults it builds fortune files for Kaamelott and Pierre Desproges. his can be changed in the Makefile.

to get a quote use `fortune kaamelott` or `fortune kaamelott pierre_desproges`

# install

```
./configure 
make 
make install
```

# development

```
aclocal # Set up an m4 environment
autoconf # Generate configure from configure.ac
./configure # Generate Makefile from Makefile.in
make distcheck # Use Makefile to build and test a tarball to distribute
```

